# Frontend environment (Vercel / CI build-time only)
# Angular does not read .env files at runtime — values are baked in at build.
#
# On Vercel: Project Settings → Environment Variables → add API_URL for Production.
# Point it at your Render backend, including the /api prefix.
#
# Example:
API_URL=https://elva-support-api.onrender.com/api

# Local development does NOT use this file.
# ng serve uses src/environments/environment.ts (localhost:3000).
